data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this lovely Davenport home! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home has a lot to offer. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining or just having family time. The home features solid counter tops throughout including a nice sized island, stainless steel appliances, a new dishwasher and ample closet space. The master retreat, bath and walk in closet will be sure to meet all your needs. The custom vanity in the master retreat is equipped with lots of drawer space. Enjoy time spent on the covered and screened in lanai. The community features a resort style pool and playground. New carpet installed 8/10/2023. The property is close to major highways and attractions. Please be sure to view the attached 3D Matterport Video Tour!
